{
  "texts": [
    "As a result, we expect that it is less likely that fair use would apply to the use of curated data.",
    "Instead, the creators of these datasets hold a copyright in the dataset and the terms of the dataset licence agreement govern the subsequent use of these data.",
    "However, it is rare in practice for a large language model (LLM) to use a single supervised dataset and often multiple datasets are compiled into collections.",
    "This further complicates the legal analysis because we find that the licence terms of many popular dataset collections are conflicting.",
    "We find that approximately 12% of the datasets we audit were annotated using OpenAI."
  ]
}